<h1>Lucerne: a web framework</h1>

<p><a href="https://travis-ci.org/eudoxia0/lucerne" ><img src="https://travis-ci.org/eudoxia0/lucerne.svg?branch=master" alt="Build Status" /></a>
<a href="https://coveralls.io/r/eudoxia0/lucerne?branch=master" ><img src="https://coveralls.io/repos/eudoxia0/lucerne/badge.svg?branch=master" alt="Coverage Status" /></a></p>

<p>Read the <a href="http://eudoxia.me/lucerne/docs/overview.html" >docs</a>.</p>

<h2>Usage</h2>

<pre><code><span class="code"><span class="paren1">(<span class="code"><i><span class="symbol">defapp</span></i> app</span>)</span>

@route app "/"
<span class="paren1">(<span class="code"><i><span class="symbol">defview</span></i> index <span class="paren2">(<span class="code"></span>)</span>
  <span class="paren2">(<span class="code">respond <span class="string">"&lt;h1&gt;Welcome to Lucerne&lt;/h1&gt;"</span></span>)</span></span>)</span>

@route app "/greet/:name"
<span class="paren1">(<span class="code"><i><span class="symbol">defview</span></i> greet <span class="paren2">(<span class="code">name</span>)</span>
  <span class="paren2">(<span class="code">respond <span class="paren3">(<span class="code">format nil <span class="string">"Hello, ~A!"</span> name</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>)</span>

<span class="paren1">(<span class="code">start app</span>)</span></span></code></pre>

